<h1>Help &gt; Block &gt; Inspect</h1>

<h2>Basics</h2>
<p>
	Turn hints on.
	You should then see a red outline around each block.
	Just hover your mouse over the blocks to see the hints pop-up at the top left of the hovred block.
</p>

<p>Click on the template path (.phtml) to open it in the editor</p>

<p>Click on the class name (Mage_*) to view info about the block.</p>